1. Download Matreshka from svn

   svn co svn://adaforge.qtada.com/matreshka/trunk/matreshka/

2. Goto design/fastcgi directory.

3. Type

   make

4. demo.fcgi executable is FastCGI application, copy it to somethere
   there you Web server can provide access to it. Don't forget make 
   matreshka/.libs/libleague.so and GNAT Run Time libraries available
   to loader.

5. Open URL in web-browser.
